{"tid":1237753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國女子邁阿密海灘腳踩海龜巢　被警方拘捕","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T15:48:55.000Z","uid":259753,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"86d1d1e7ee707f7c6814e1e772b9ba188b25b515","tid":1237753,"uid":259753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:33:21.000Z","msg":"中國女子邁阿密海灘腳踩海龜巢　被警方拘捕<br />\n<br />\n【動物專訊】每一千隻小海龜，估計只得一隻可以生存到成年，所以很多國家都有法例保護海龜在海灘生蛋，但一名中國女子於邁阿密海灘被人發現以木棍桶海龜巢，又赤腳四處用力踩，6月15日被美國警方以侵害海龜的罪名拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n全文見：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/2019/06/17/06171/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2F06171%2F&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYYsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=97d62c6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkanimalpost.com/2019/06/17/06171/</a><br />\n<br />\n應該懲罰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />踩返爆佢個卵巢 sor係有d噁心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0874c5d794301945c13a62c94f4aebdbdb494ec","tid":1237753,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"閹撚咗隻狗乸啦"},{"pid":"af4653bfd4b94ace80e2c3ea23e22b5cc5c2d19e","tid":1237753,"uid":2766,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"d大陸哩真係十個十個都仆街<br />\n唔係偷野搶野抄野假野<br />\n就柯屎柯尿搞破壞<br />\n正一垃圾人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f5724995a0b48a14a664c5cebb0e5173dc1cf7","tid":1237753,"uid":16567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f0874c5d794301945c13a62c94f4aebdbdb494ec","tid":1237753,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:34:31.000Z","msg":"閹撚咗隻狗乸啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"塞返2-30個龜蛋入佢個閪度"},{"pid":"a06179c5ad811ac60d000e45063bd40f3ea2e5b7","tid":1237753,"uid":145238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03f5724995a0b48a14a664c5cebb0e5173dc1cf